OL,5,G1300 Inside the Ambulance
OL,6,     FThe West Midlands crews treat a
OL,7,     Fpensioner whose heart rate is so
OL,8,     Ferratic they are worried he might
OL,9,     Fhave a heart attack on the way to
OL,10,     Fthe hospital.
OL,11,G1400 Inside the Ambulance
OL,12,     FCrews from West Midlands Ambulance
OL,13,     FService attend a diabetic who has
OL,14,     Fcollapsed at home, reassure the
OL,15,     Fwife of a man with heart problems
OL,16,     Fand keep up the spirits of a woman
OL,17,     Fwith womb cancer.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
