OL,5,G1500 Inside the Ambulance
OL,6,     FThe paramedics treat a young mum
OL,7,     Fwith severe stomach pains, take a
OL,8,     Fbreathless pensioner to hospital
OL,9,     Fand attend an elderly lady with
OL,10,     Fdementia whose nose will not stop
OL,11,     Fbleeding.
OL,12,G1600 Inside the Ambulance
OL,13,     FDudley crews attend a man with
OL,14,     Fheart failure and sepsis, as well
OL,15,     Fas a transgender patient who's in
OL,16,     Fa lot of pain from an old injury.
OL,17,     FIn Stoke, a patient has a panic
OL,18,     Fattack in the ambulance.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
